		<description><![CDATA[<p>In light of the news that New York is joining the small group of states that allow same-sex marriages, and in response to the fear-addled <a href="http://twitter.com/#!/albertmohler" target="_blank">tweets</a> of Al Mohler upon hearing the news, I wanted to repost this <a href="http://www.patheos.com/Resources/Additional-Resources/Stop-Fighting-to-Save-Marriage-Jonathan-Fitzgerald-02-23-2011.html" target="_blank">column</a> I wrote for Patheos back in February. No matter your take on [...]]]></description>
